Name: Doctor
Summary: A military doctor embarks on a journey to track down his former fiancee's kidnapped niece. His mission then leads him to the heart of a human trafficking ring in Goa.

Name: Sethupathi
Summary: While conducting an investigation into the mysterious death of a fellow officer, a cop's own reputation is questioned when a suspect in his custody is shot.

Name: Alai Payuthey
Summary: Karthik and Shakti marry against the wishes of their families and start their new life. However, they soon realise that marriage is not the bed of roses they had imagined it would be.

Name: Fast & Furious
Summary: Fast & Furious is a media franchise centered on a series of action films that are largely concerned with illegal street racing, heists, spies and family. The franchise also includes short films, a television series, live shows, video games and theme park attractions. It is distributed by Universal Pictures.
